{"id":"c1b996231b82079f5aeb4e40c5291203414c1f90","url":"https://www.businessinsider.com/google-q2-2026-earnings-historic-negative-cash-flow-ai-costs-2026-7","title":"Google reports historic negative cash flow amid AI costs","site_name":"Buzzing","source":"www.businessinsider.com","byline":"Hugh Langley","excerpt":"Google reports negative cash flow due to AI spending, raising capex forecast as infrastructure costs rise.","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><section data-content-container=\"\" role=\"main\">\n\n  \n    \n  \n    <div data-load-strategy=\"disable-lazy\" data-component-type=\"post-top\">\n  \n        \n        \n        \n          <section id=\"post-headline\">\n            <h2>Even Google couldn't out-earn its AI spending this quarter</h2>\n        \n          </section>\n          \n          \n          \n            <div data-component-type=\"post-byline\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-byline\" data-e2e-name=\"byline\">\n                      <p><span>By</span>\n                              \n                              \n                              \n                                <span data-e2e-name=\"Hugh Langley\">\n                              \n                                  <span>\n                                    <a data-e2e-name=\"byline-author-name\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\">Hugh Langley</a>        \n                                <span data-disable-for-sooth-user=\"\" data-component-type=\"follow-button\" data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" role=\"tooltip\" data-tooltip-position=\"middle\" data-tooltip-active=\"false\" data-state=\"\" data-topic-type=\"author\" data-topic-slug=\"hugh-langley\" data-topic-link=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-topic-label=\"Hugh Langley\" data-topic-location=\"byline\" data-topic-shortened-label=\"Hugh\" data-topic-image=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Headshot of Hugh Langley&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:3394,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;Insider&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:2263},&quot;links&quot;:{&quot;self&quot;:&quot;https://i.insider.com/6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;}}\">\n                                  \n                                \n                                  <div>\n                                    <p>\n                                        You're currently following this author!\n                                 Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n                                    </p>\n                                  </div>\n                                  \n                                </span>\n                                  </span>\n                                </span>  </p>\n                    </div>\n      </div>\n\n  <section>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n      <section id=\"post-body\" data-component-type=\"post-body\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-lock-content=\"\">\n            \n            \n            \n            <div data-component-type=\"post-hero\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\">\n                  <figure data-type=\"img\" data-e2e-name=\"image-figure-image\" data-media-container=\"image\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ImageObject\">\n                      <div>\n                        <meta itemprop=\"contentUrl\" content=\"https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=1200\">\n                        <p><img src=\"https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=700\" srcset=\"https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=400&format=jpeg&auto=webp 400w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=500&format=jpeg&auto=webp 500w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=700&format=jpeg&auto=webp 700w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=1000&format=jpeg&auto=webp 1000w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=1300&format=jpeg&auto=webp 1300w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=2000&format=jpeg&auto=webp 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 900px\" alt=\"Google CEO Sundar Pichai\" decoding=\"sync\">\n                      </p></div>\n                  \n                    <span>\n                          <span>\n                            \n                            <label for=\"caption-drawer-btn\">\n                                      </label>\n                    \n                            <figcaption data-e2e-name=\"image-caption\">\n                              <span>Google CEO Sundar Pichai.</span>\n                              <span>\n                                <span data-e2e-name=\"image-source\" itemprop=\"creditText\">Bloomberg/Getty Images</span>          </span>\n                            </figcaption>\n                          </span>\n                    </span></figure>\n            </div>\n    \n    \n    \n            \n      \n              \n      \n      \n              \n              \n              \n              \n      \n            \n      \n        <section data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" data-component-type=\"image-modal\" data-track-content=\"\" data-post-type=\"story\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-body-content\">\n                  \n                      <p>The bill for Google's AI spending spree is coming due.</p><p>Google said Wednesday that its free cash flow for the second quarter turned to negative $5.9 billion, as the company's capital expenditures continue to rise.</p><p>It marks the first time the company has reported negative free cash flow in decades, per AlphaSense, a signal of how much money Google is spending on AI data centers and hardware.</p><p>Google, Amazon, Microsoft, and Meta had already planned to spend more than <a target=\"_self\" rel=\"\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/big-tech-earnings-microsoft-ai-investment-capex-plan-2026-4\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\"><u>$700 billion in capex</u></a> this year, and that number only seems to be ticking up.</p><p>Google said it now expects to spend $195 billion to $205 billion in capex for full-year 2026, up from its previous estimate of $180 billion to $190 billion.</p><p>Anat Ashkenazi, Google's chief financial officer, said the company expects capex spend to increase \"significantly\" in 2027.</p><p>On Wednesday, <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/tesla-q2-earnings-updates-tsla-stock-elon-musk-spacex-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">Tesla reported</a> negative cash flow for the first time in more than two years, as Elon Musk's company also ramps up spending on AI infrastructure.</p><p>There's also a question about how far these dollars actually stretch compared to a year ago. Some analysts reckon there's inflation due to <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/big-tech-spending-capex-earnings-season-memory-prices-ai-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">higher costs of memory chips</a> and other materials, which make it more expensive to build out capacity.</p><p>All things considered, investors probably expect Google's cash flow to remain in the red for quite some time — even as the company continues to report strong revenue gains.</p>\n                  \n                  \n                  </section>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n      </section>\n\n    \n    <!-- Included desktop \"post-aside\" -->  \n\n    \n      \n      <section data-component-type=\"post-bottom\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-bottom\">\n        <section>\n    \n    \n            \n            \n    \n              \n                \n                \n                <section data-component-type=\"dad-related-posts\" data-delay-third-party-scripts=\"true\" data-size=\"4\" data-min-size=\"3\" data-container-index=\"\" data-included-verticals=\"tech\" data-placement=\"post-bottom\" data-track-marfeel=\"dad-related-posts-post-bottom\" data-excluded-verticals=\"bi-video\" data-root-margin=\"250px 0px\" data-track-view=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;end_of_article_recirc&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;subscription_experience&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\">\n                    <P>\n                      <h2>\n                        Read next\n                      </h2>\n                    </P>\n              \n              \n                  \n                </section>\n          \n          \n        <div data-component-type=\"post-bottom-authors\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-track-view=\"{&quot;subscription_experience&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;author_bio&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;module_in_view&quot;}\" data-track-click-shared=\"{&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;author_bio&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;navigation&quot;}\">\n                <a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;index&quot;:1}\">\n                      <div data-slug=\"hugh-langley\">\n                          <p><img data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 1 1'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" src=\"https://i.insider.com/6556827