uot;,&quot;container&quot;:&quot;taboola-below-main-column&quot;,&quot;placement&quot;:&quot;below-main-column&quot;,&quot;onlyOn&quot;:&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;target_type&quot;:&quot;mix&quot;}}\" data-load-strategy=\"defer\">\n                \n              </vendor-taboola>\n          \n          <!-- Excluded mobile \"taboola\" --></section>\n    \n      </section>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  <back-to-home data-component-type=\"back-to-home\" data-load-strategy=\"defer\" data-only-on=\"mobile\">\n    \n    \n    \n  \n    \n  </back-to-home>\n</section></DIV>","content_text":"Even Google couldn't out-earn its AI spending this quarter By Hugh Langley You're currently following this author! Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email. Google CEO Sundar Pichai. Bloomberg/Getty Images The bill for Google's AI spending spree is coming due.Google said Wednesday that its free cash flow for the second quarter turned to negative $5.9 billion, as the company's capital expenditures continue to rise.It marks the first time the company has reported negative free cash flow in decades, per AlphaSense, a signal of how much money Google is spending on AI data centers and hardware.Google, Amazon, Microsoft, and Meta had already planned to spend more than $700 billion in capex this year, and that number only seems to be ticking up.Google said it now expects to spend $195 billion to $205 billion in capex for full-year 2026, up from its previous estimate of $180 billion to $190 billion.Anat Ashkenazi, Google's chief financial officer, said the company expects capex spend to increase \"significantly\" in 2027.On Wednesday, Tesla reported negative cash flow for the first time in more than two years, as Elon Musk's company also ramps up spending on AI infrastructure.There's also a question about how far these dollars actually stretch compared to a year ago. Some analysts reckon there's inflation due to higher costs of memory chips and other materials, which make it more expensive to build out capacity.All things considered, investors probably expect Google's cash flow to remain in the red for quite some time — even as the company continues to report strong revenue gains. Read next Hugh Langley You're currently following this author! Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email. Google AI Alphabet More Technology Earnings Big Tech","fetched_at":"2026-07-23T22:25:45.243Z","ok":true,"blocks":[{"html_en":"<h2>Even Google couldn't out-earn its AI spending this quarter</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Even Google couldn't out-earn its AI spending this quarter","zh":"即使是谷歌本季度的人工智能支出也无法盈利"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>By</span>\n                              \n                              \n                              \n                                <span data-e2e-name=\"Hugh Langley\">\n                              \n                                  <span>\n                                    <a data-e2e-name=\"byline-author-name\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\">Hugh Langley</a>        \n                                <span data-disable-for-sooth-user=\"\" data-component-type=\"follow-button\" data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" role=\"tooltip\" data-tooltip-position=\"middle\" data-tooltip-active=\"false\" data-state=\"\" data-topic-type=\"author\" data-topic-slug=\"hugh-langley\" data-topic-link=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-topic-label=\"Hugh Langley\" data-topic-location=\"byline\" data-topic-shortened-label=\"Hugh\" data-topic-image=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Headshot of Hugh Langley&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:3394,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;Insider&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:2263},&quot;links&quot;:{&quot;self&quot;:&quot;https://i.insider.com/6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;}}\">\n                                  \n                                \n                                  <div>\n                                    <p>\n                                        You're currently following this author!\n                                 Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n                                    </p>\n                                  </div>\n                                  \n                                </span>\n                                  </span>\n                                </span>  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"By Hugh Langley You're currently following this author!","zh":"作者：Hugh Langley 您目前正在关注该作者！"},{"en":"Want to unfollow?","zh":"想要取消关注吗？"},{"en":"Unsubscribe via the link in your email.","zh":"通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>\n                                        You're currently following this author!\n                                 Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n                                    </p>","sentences":[{"en":"You're currently following this author!","zh":"您目前正在关注该作者！"},{"en":"Want to unfollow?","zh":"想要取消关注吗？"},{"en":"Unsubscribe via the link in your email.","zh":"通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。"}]},{"html_en":"<figcaption data-e2e-name=\"image-caption\">\n                              <span>Google CEO Sundar Pichai.</span>\n                              <span>\n                                <span data-e2e-name=\"image-source\" itemprop=\"creditText\">Bloomberg/Getty Images</span>          </span>\n                            </figcaption>","sentences":[{"en":"Google CEO Sundar Pichai.","zh":"谷歌首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊。"},{"en":"Bloomberg/Getty Images","zh":"彭博社/盖蒂图片社"}]},{"html_en":"<p>The bill for Google's AI spending spree is coming due.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"The bill for Google's AI spending spree is coming due.","zh":"谷歌人工智能支出热潮的账单即将到期。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Google said Wednesday that its free cash flow for the second quarter turned to negative $5.9 billion, as the company's capital expenditures continue to rise.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Google said Wednesday that its free cash flow for the second quarter turned to negative $5.9 billion, as the company's capital expenditures continue to rise.","zh":"谷歌周三表示，随着公司资本支出持续增加，第二季度自由现金流转为负 59 亿美元。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>It marks the first time the company has reported negative free cash flow in decades, per AlphaSense, a signal of how much money Google is spending on AI data centers and hardware.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"It marks the first time the company has reported negative free cash flow in decades, per AlphaSense, a signal of how much money Google is spending on AI data centers and hardware.","zh":"根据 AlphaSense 的说法，这标志着该公司几十年来首次报告负自由现金流，这表明谷歌在人工智能数据中心和硬件上花费了多少钱。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Google, Amazon, Microsoft, and Meta had already planned to spend more than <a target=\"_self\" rel=\"\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/big-tech-earnings-microsoft-ai-investment-capex-plan-2026-4\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\"><u>$700 billion in capex</u></a> this year, and that number only seems to be ticking up.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Google, Amazon, Microsoft, and Meta had already planned to spend more than $700 billion in capex this year, and that number only seems to be ticking up.","zh":"谷歌、亚马逊、微软和 Meta 已经计划今年的资本支出超过 7000 亿美元，而且这个数字似乎还在不断增加。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Google said it now expects to spend $195 billion to $205 billion in capex for full-year 2026, up from its previous estimate of $180 billion to $190 billion.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Google said it now expects to spend $195 billion to $205 billion in capex for full-year 2026, up from its previous estimate of $180 billion to $190 billion.","zh":"谷歌表示，目前预计 2026 年全年资本支出为 1950 亿美元至 2050 亿美元，高于之前预计的 1800 亿美元至 1900 亿美元。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Anat Ashkenazi, Google's chief financial officer, said the company expects capex spend to increase \"significantly\" in 2027.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Anat Ashkenazi, Google's chief financial officer, said the company expects capex spend to increase \"significantly\" in 2027.","zh":"谷歌首席财务官阿纳特·阿什肯纳齐 (Anat Ashkenazi) 表示，该公司预计 2027 年资本支出将“大幅”增加。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>On Wednesday, <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/tesla-q2-earnings-updates-tsla-stock-elon-musk-spacex-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">Tesla reported</a> negative cash flow for the first time in more than two years, as Elon Musk's company also ramps up spending on AI infrastructure.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"On Wednesday, Tesla reported negative cash flow for the first time in more than two years, as Elon Musk's company also ramps up spending on AI infrastructure.","zh":"周三，特斯拉报告两年多来首次出现负现金流，埃隆·马斯克的公司也加大了人工智能基础设施的支出。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>There's also a question about how far these dollars actually stretch compared to a year ago. Some analysts reckon there's inflation due to <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/big-tech-spending-capex-earnings-season-memory-prices-ai-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">higher costs of memory chips</a> and other materials, which make it more expensive to build out capacity.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"There's also a question about how far these dollars actually stretch compared to a year ago.","zh":"还有一个问题是，与一年前相比，这些美元实际上增长了多少。"},{"en":"Some analysts reckon there's inflation due to higher costs of memory chips and other materials, which make it more expensive to build out capacity.","zh":"一些分析师认为，通货膨胀是由于存储芯片和其他材料的成本上涨造成的，这使得建设产能的成本更高。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>All things considered, investors probably expect Google's cash flow to remain in the red for quite some time — even as the company continues to report strong revenue gains.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"All things considered, investors probably expect Google's cash flow to remain in the red for quite some time — even as the company continues to report strong revenue gains.","zh":"考虑到所有因素，投资者可能预计谷歌的现金流将在相当长一段时间内保持亏损状态——尽管该公司继续报告强劲的收入增长。"}]},{"html_en":"<h2>\n                        Read next\n                      </h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Read next","zh":"阅读下一篇"}]},{"html_en":"<p><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;index&quot;:1}\">Hugh Langley</a>\n        \n                \n          <span data-disable-for-sooth-user=\"\" data-component-type=\"follow-button\" data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" role=\"tooltip\" data-tooltip-position=\"middle\" data-tooltip-active=\"false\" data-state=\"\" data-topic-type=\"author\" data-topic-slug=\"hugh-langley\" data-topic-link=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-topic-label=\"Hugh Langley\" data-topic-location=\"author_bio\" data-topic-shortened-label=\"Hugh\" data-topic-image=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Headshot of Hugh Langley&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:3394,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;Insider&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:2263},&quot;links&quot;:{&quot;self&quot;:&quot;https://i.insider.com/6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;}}\">\n            \n          \n            <div>\n              <p>\n                  You're currently following this author!\n           Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            \n          </span>\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Hugh Langley You're currently following this author!","zh":"休·兰利 您目前正在关注该作者！"},{"en":"Want to unfollow?","zh":"想要取消关注吗？"},{"en":"Unsubscribe via the link in your email.","zh":"通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>\n                  You're currently following this author!\n           Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n              </p>","sentences":[{"en":"You're currently following this author!","zh":"您目前正在关注该作者！"},{"en":"Want to unfollow?","zh":"想要取消关注吗？"},{"en":"Unsubscribe via the link in your email.","zh":"通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。"}]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                  <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/google\" title=\"Google\">Google</a>\n                </li>","sentences":[{"en":"Google","zh":"谷歌"}]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                  <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/ai\" title=\"AI\">AI</a>\n                </li>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                  <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/alphabet\" title=\"Alphabet\">Alphabet</a>\n                </li>","sentences":[{"en":"Alphabet","zh":"字母"}]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                  <span data-track-click=\"{&quot;click_text&quot;:&quot;More&quot;,&quot;click_path&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">More </span>\n                </li>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                    <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/technology\" title=\"Technology\">Technology</a>\n                  </li>","sentences":[{"en":"Technology","zh":"技术"}]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                    <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/earnings\" title=\"Earnings\">Earnings</a>\n                  </li>","sentences":[{"en":"Earnings","zh":"收益"}]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                    <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/big-tech\" title=\"Big Tech\">Big Tech</a>\n                  </li>","sentences":[{"en":"Big Tech","zh":"大型科技公司"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><section data-content-container=\"\" role=\"main\">\n\n  \n    \n  \n    <div data-load-strategy=\"disable-lazy\" data-component-type=\"post-top\">\n  \n        \n        \n        \n          <section id=\"post-headline\">\n            <h2>即使是谷歌本季度的人工智能支出也无法盈利</h2>\n        \n          </section>\n          \n          \n          \n            <div data-component-type=\"post-byline\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-byline\" data-e2e-name=\"byline\">\n                      <p>作者：Hugh Langley 您目前正在关注该作者！ 想要取消关注吗？ 通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。</p>\n                    </div>\n      </div>\n\n  <section>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n      <section id=\"post-body\" data-component-type=\"post-body\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-lock-content=\"\">\n            \n            \n            \n            <div data-component-type=\"post-hero\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\">\n                  <figure data-type=\"img\" data-e2e-name=\"image-figure-image\" data-media-container=\"image\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ImageObject\">\n                      <div>\n                        <meta itemprop=\"contentUrl\" content=\"https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=1200\">\n                        <p><img src=\"https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=700\" srcset=\"https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=400&format=jpeg&auto=webp 400w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=500&format=jpeg&auto=webp 500w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=700&format=jpeg&auto=webp 700w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=1000&format=jpeg&auto=webp 1000w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=1300&format=jpeg&auto=webp 1300w, https://i.insider.com/6a61383054f9875261778964?width=2000&format=jpeg&auto=webp 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 900px\" alt=\"Google CEO Sundar Pichai\" decoding=\"sync\">\n                      </p></div>\n                  \n                    <span>\n                          <span>\n                            \n                            <label for=\"caption-drawer-btn\">\n                                      </label>\n                    \n                            <figcaption data-e2e-name=\"image-caption\">谷歌首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊。 彭博社/盖蒂图片社</figcaption>\n                          </span>\n                    </span></figure>\n            </div>\n    \n    \n    \n            \n      \n              \n      \n      \n              \n              \n              \n              \n      \n            \n      \n        <section data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" data-component-type=\"image-modal\" data-track-content=\"\" data-post-type=\"story\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-body-content\">\n                  \n                      <p>谷歌人工智能支出热潮的账单即将到期。</p><p>谷歌周三表示，随着公司资本支出持续增加，第二季度自由现金流转为负 59 亿美元。</p><p>根据 AlphaSense 的说法，这标志着该公司几十年来首次报告负自由现金流，这表明谷歌在人工智能数据中心和硬件上花费了多少钱。</p><p>谷歌、亚马逊、微软和 Meta 已经计划今年的资本支出超过 7000 亿美元，而且这个数字似乎还在不断增加。</p><p>谷歌表示，目前预计 2026 年全年资本支出为 1950 亿美元至 2050 亿美元，高于之前预计的 1800 亿美元至 1900 亿美元。</p><p>谷歌首席财务官阿纳特·阿什肯纳齐 (Anat Ashkenazi) 表示，该公司预计 2027 年资本支出将“大幅”增加。</p><p>周三，特斯拉报告两年多来首次出现负现金流，埃隆·马斯克的公司也加大了人工智能基础设施的支出。</p><p>还有一个问题是，与一年前相比，这些美元实际上增长了多少。 一些分析师认为，通货膨胀是由于存储芯片和其他材料的成本上涨造成的，这使得建设产能的成本更高。</p><p>考虑到所有因素，投资者可能预计谷歌的现金流将在相当长一段时间内保持亏损状态——尽管该公司继续报告强劲的收入增长。</p>\n                  \n                  \n                  </section>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n      </section>\n\n    \n    <!-- Included desktop \"post-aside\" -->  \n\n    \n      \n      <section data-component-type=\"post-bottom\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-bottom\">\n        <section>\n    \n    \n            \n            \n    \n              \n                \n                \n                <section data-component-type=\"dad-related-posts\" data-delay-third-party-scripts=\"true\" data-size=\"4\" data-min-size=\"3\" data-container-index=\"\" data-included-verticals=\"tech\" data-placement=\"post-bottom\" data-track-marfeel=\"dad-related-posts-post-bottom\" data-excluded-verticals=\"bi-video\" data-root-margin=\"250px 0px\" data-track-view=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;end_of_article_recirc&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;subscription_experience&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\">\n                    <p>\n                      </p><h2>阅读下一篇</h2>\n                    <p></p>\n              \n              \n                  \n                </section>\n          \n          \n        <div data-component-type=\"post-bottom-authors\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-track-view=\"{&quot;subscription_experience&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;author_bio&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;module_in_view&quot;}\" data-track-click-shared=\"{&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;author_bio&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;navigation&quot;}\">\n                <a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;index&quot;:1}\">\n                      <div data-slug=\"hugh-langley\">\n                          <p><img data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 1 1'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" src=\"https://i.insider.com/6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0?crop=1:1&width=256&format=jpeg&auto=webp\" alt=\"Headshot of Hugh Langley\">\n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        </p>  </div>\n                </a>\n        \n              <p>休·兰利 您目前正在关注该作者！ 想要取消关注吗？ 通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。</p></div>\n    \n          \n          \n          \n          <div data-component-type=\"post-category-tags\" data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-category-tags\">\n            <ul data-track-click-shared=\"{&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;navigation&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&qu